sql: SELECT COUNT(CASE WHEN booking_status='IssuedBusiness' THEN 1 END) as bookings FROM sme_analytics.sme_leadbookingrevenue WHERE investmenttypeid IN (5) AND DATE(bookingdate) = CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1' DAY AND paymentstatus = 300
explanation: Metric: bookings; Products: [5]; Time: yesterday; Online payments only (paymentstatus=300)
